<h1 class="center-align">Welcome to MindBook</h1>
<div class="row center-align">
  <div class="col s12 m6 offset-m3">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="card-title">Hi there!</span>
        <p>This is a social network app build with RoR. <br>
          It has some useful functionality and security features. <br>
          Feel free to join and play with the app</p>
